articles.description: Andre Spight, Jalen Sanders and Jordan Davis combined to score 70 points and Northern Colorado routed Northern Arizona, 95-60 on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Northern Colorado trio score 70, rout Northern Arizona 95-60

articles.description: Deandre Ayton scores 25 points and grabs 16 rebounds as No. 17 Arizona holds off No. 25 Arizona State, 77-70.
articles.headline: Arizona completes season sweep of Arizona State

images.caption: Deandre Ayton scores 25 points and grabs 16 rebounds as No. 17 Arizona holds off No. 25 Arizona State, 77-70.
images.name: Arizona completes season sweep of Arizona State

articles.description: Freshman Ledarrius Brewer scored 34 points with seven 3-pointers -- both career-highs -- and Southeast Missouri State jumped ahead early to defeat Eastern Illinois 80-73 Thursday night.
articles.headline: Brewer scores 34, paces Southeast Missouri St. to 80-73 win

articles.description: Tony Carr scores a game-high 30 points and Penn State sweeps the season series with Ohio State, winning 19 games for the first time since 2010-11.
articles.headline: PSU upsets No. 8 OSU by 23 points

images.caption: Tony Carr scores a game-high 30 points and Penn State sweeps the season series with Ohio State, winning 19 games for the first time since 2010-11.
images.name: PSU upsets No. 8 OSU by 23 points

articles.description: C.J. Burks scored a career-high 36 points with six 3-pointers, Jon Elmore added 28 points, six assists and seven rebounds and Marshall defeated Rice 93-80 Thursday night.
articles.headline: Burks scores 36, Marshall overtakes Rice 93-80

articles.description: Delano Spencer sank a career-best seven 3-pointers on his way to a career-high 32 points and Tennessee State held off Morehead State 83-74 on Thursday night for its seventh straight victory.
articles.headline: Spencer sparks Tennessee State past Morehead State 83-74
